			<td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=107343&amp;sid=3548031bdd81678bfa170707128637c5#107343"><img src="templates/eqluclin/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Sat Feb 12, 2005 7:51 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: LokiTorrent operator ordered to pay 1 million dollar fine</span></td>
				<td width="30%" valign="top" nowrap="nowrap" align="right"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=107343&amp;sid=3548031bdd81678bfa170707128637c5"><img src="templates/eqluclin/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>     </td></tr></table></td>
